 convective zone is located.\n  We found that $P_{ cyc}$ is about constant and that <IQR> decreases with the\nstellare age in the range 4-95 Myr. We investigated the magnetic activity of AB\nDor A by merging ASAS time-series with previous long-term photometric data. We\nestimated the length of the AB Dor A primary cycle as $P_{ cyc} = 16.78 \\pm 2\n\\rm yr$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 24 Jun 2017 10:59:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
