traightforward and logically satisfying method for\nmoving back and forth between well-studied number systems like $\\mathbb{R}$ and\nvery abstract number systems, such as an $\\eta_{_{\\omega^\\omega}}$-field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jun 2017 18:22:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Jun 2017 23:07:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-03"}
